	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use &quot;oe MT_Baptism&quot; and then &quot;oe MT_Court&quot; to start the baptism and teleport to the courtroom.&#xD;&#xA;- Walk to the room on the right - the abattoir - to find Valeria chained up there and saying this AD once you're nearby. She will play an AD every time after the cultists do two chants." />
